        en: {
            intro: 'TSH-100 single shaft solid waste shredder is a professional and reliable shredding system designed for industrial applications requiring high capacity and large-scale recycling facilities.',
            paragraph1: 'TSH-100 single shaft shredder offers a wide 1000x1300 mm shredding area with powerful 30-75 kW motor options. With 1200-1800 kg/hour processing capacity, it meets the plastic shredder, fabric shredder, pallet shredder and paper shredder needs of large-scale production facilities. This system, which easily shreds thick-walled plastics, large wood pieces, industrial containers, IBC tanks, heavy textile waste, large volume packaging materials and composite waste, provides industrial standard performance as plastic crusher and scrap plastic crushing machine.',
            paragraph2: 'TSH-100 solid waste shredder, equipped with advanced PLC control panel, touch screen operator interface, remote monitoring and maintenance reminder systems, plays an important role in recycling and waste management. Thanks to 1000 mm rotor, 40 premium quality hardened steel blades and hydraulic pusher system, it guarantees continuous and uninterrupted production. Automatic reverse operation and intelligent load management provide maximum efficiency in plastic shredding machine and recycling crusher applications. Operates with high torque and low speed combination to safely process challenging materials.',
            paragraph3: 'MT Makina TSH-100 single shaft shredder is an ideal solution for large plastic recycling facilities, wooden pallet manufacturers, composite material processors, industrial waste management companies and textile recycling factories. Thanks to its modular structure, it can be integrated with discharge screws, conveyor belts, metal separators, pipe magnets and separators. Supported by CE certified safety standards and 2-year warranty. Low investment cost and fast return on investment in terms of solid waste shredder prices.',
            paragraph4: 'With single shaft shredder technology, TSH-100 provides superior results in plastic scrap crusher, bale shredder, rubber shredder and scrap tire shredder applications. Thanks to optimized cutter geometry and wide screen surface, it provides homogeneous shredding and low energy consumption. Delivers reliable performance even in harsh conditions thanks to powerful drive motors and durable cutting tools. Different output sizes can be adjusted with replaceable screen system (20-100 mm).',
            paragraph5: 'TSH-100 single shaft solid waste shredder minimizes operating costs with energy-efficient special blade design and automatic shutdown feature. This system, which offers competitive pricing in plastic crusher prices, is preferred for large capacity recycling projects. Requires minimum maintenance with automatic lubrication system, reinforced bearing structure and solid steel body. Can also be successfully used in electronic waste, e-waste processing and municipal waste management projects.',
            paragraph6: 'Providing sustainability in waste management, TSH-100 offers high efficiency, environmental benefits and economic advantages to businesses by optimizing recycling processes. As Turkey\'s leading shredder manufacturer MT Makina, we offer a wide product range with single shaft solid waste shredder, double shaft shredder and four shaft shredder models. Contact us for plastic shredder price quotes and technical consultancy services. TSH-100 is the recommended professional-grade shredding solution for large-scale industrial projects.'
        },
